                <p class="text-white mt-3 px-3">
                    More than a platform — it’s your campus hub for collaboration, learning, and growth.
                    Discover new experiences, share ideas, and thrive together.
                </p>
                <div style="margin-top: -30px;">
                    <% if (!user) { %>
                        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" onclick="window.location.href='/register'">Start
