                            Because great ideas grow stronger when shared together.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="margin-top: 100px;">
                    <div>
                        <div class="posterHeading">
                            <p>Build Your</p>
                            <p style="color: #97a7b6;">Professional Network</p>
                        </div>
